633
01:00:46,050 --> 01:00:48,100
Except for that part of naming the gravedigger after me.

634
01:00:48,180 --> 01:00:50,060
You can leave that in.

635
01:00:51,890 --> 01:00:54,650
I really value your criticism

636
01:00:54,730 --> 01:00:56,480
but maybe we're being a little hasty here.

637
01:00:56,570 --> 01:00:59,360
Paul, what you've written just isn't fair.

638
01:00:59,440 --> 01:01:00,480
Not fair?

639
01:01:00,570 --> 01:01:01,610
That's right.

640
01:01:01,900 --> 01:01:03,360
When I was growing up in Bakersfield,

641
01:01:03,450 --> 01:01:04,820
my favorite thing in all the world

