694
01:04:01,580 --> 01:04:02,750
Have to wait.

695
01:04:02,830 --> 01:04:05,960
Will she still love him with that special, perfect love?

696
01:04:06,050 --> 01:04:07,460
You'll have to wait.

697
01:04:07,550 --> 01:04:08,840
Not even a hint?

698
01:04:08,920 --> 01:04:10,050
Uh-uh.

699
01:04:10,130 --> 01:04:11,340
