774
01:09:00,880 --> 01:09:05,550
To Misery and to Annie Wilkes, who brought her back to life.

775
01:09:06,890 --> 01:09:09,930
Paul, I get goose bumps every time I think about it!

776
01:09:10,310 --> 01:09:12,020
